"When a colleague shares an email folder with you and opts to send a "
"notification, you will receive an automatic email. Simply click the "
"**ACCEPT** button at the end of the email to seamlessly add the folder to"
" your inbox. If your colleague did not select the notification option, "
"you can manually add the share by following these steps:"
msgstr ""
