msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:29
msgid ""
"Enter a keyword in the search box, such as a term used in an email "
"subject or body that you are searching for."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:30
msgid "Click the button next to the search box with the magnifying glass icon."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:31
msgid ""
"Your search results will appear on the left side of a list, beside the "
"total number of items loaded."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:34
msgid "Using Advanced Search to Filter Your Search"
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:36
msgid ""
"This is performed using the search feature you can select from the left "
"sidebar."
msgstr ""

