msgid "Select the **Search feature** from your left sidebar."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:45
msgid ""
"Select the search category (i.e., Mails, Calendars, Contacts, Files) from"
" the drop-down menu next to the **NEW** button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:46
msgid "Click on **ADVANCED FILTERS** on the left side. A new window appears."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:47
msgid "Select different filters to refine your search results."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:48
msgid "Click the **SEARCH** button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:50
msgid ""
"Filters for refining search results vary depending on the category you "
"select in step 2. For instance, in the Mails category, the filters "
"include:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:52
msgid "**Attachment**: Search in emails that have an attachment."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:53
msgid "**Flagged**: Search in flagged emails."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:54
msgid "**Unread**: Search in unread email items."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:55
msgid "**Include shared folders**: Include shared items in the search."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:56
msgid "**Keyword**: Search for specific terms used in the email body."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:57
msgid "**Subject**: Search in email subjects."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:58
msgid "**From**: Search for emails received from a specific email address."
msgstr ""

#: ../../search/toc.rst:59
msgid "**To**: Search for emails sent to a specific email address."
msgstr ""
"**À** : Rechercher les e‑mails envoyés à une adresse électronique "
"spécifique."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:60
msgid ""
"**Attachment type**: Search for specific attachment formats such as PDF, "
"text document, images, etc."
msgstr ""
"**Type de pièce jointe** : Rechercher des formats de pièces jointes "
"spécifiques tels que PDF, document texte, images, etc."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:61
msgid ""
"**Status of e-mail item**: Search for emails with specific status such as"
" read, unread, flagged, etc."
msgstr ""
"**Statut de l'élément e‑mail** : Rechercher les e‑mails avec un statut "
"précis (lu, non lu, signalé, etc.)."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:62
msgid ""
"**Size smaller than (MB)**: Search for emails with a size smaller than a "
"specified number in MB."
msgstr ""
"**Taille inférieure à (Mo)** : Rechercher les e‑mails dont la taille est "
"inférieure au nombre indiqué en Mo."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:63
msgid ""
"**Size larger than (MB)**: Search for emails with a size larger than a "
"specified number in MB."
msgstr ""
"**Taille supérieure à (Mo)** : Rechercher les e‑mails dont la taille "
"dépasse le nombre indiqué en Mo."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:64
msgid "**Sent before**: Search for emails sent before the specified date."
msgstr "**Envoyé avant** : Rechercher les e‑mails envoyés avant la date spécifiée."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:65
msgid "**Sent after**: Search for emails sent after the specified date."
msgstr "**Envoyé après** : Rechercher les e‑mails envoyés après la date spécifiée."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:66
msgid "**Sent on**: Search for emails sent exactly on the specified date."
msgstr ""
"**Envoyé le** : Rechercher les e‑mails envoyés exactement à la date "
"spécifiée."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:67
msgid "**Tag**: Search for emails or contacts that have a specific tag."
msgstr ""
"**Étiquette** : Rechercher les e‑mails ou contacts portant une étiquette "
"spécifique."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:68
msgid "**Is contained in**: Limit the search to selected folders."
msgstr "**Contenu dans** : Limiter la recherche aux dossiers sélectionnés."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:71
msgid "Advanced Search Syntax"
msgstr "Syntaxe de recherche avancée"

#: ../../search/toc.rst:73
msgid ""
"**Syntax**: You can search for various items such as words, names, phone "
"numbers, or domain names. However, when conducting content searches, it "
"is essential to follow certain rules."
msgstr ""
"**Syntaxe** : Vous pouvez rechercher divers éléments tels que mots, noms,"
" numéros de téléphone ou noms de domaine. Cependant, lors des recherches "
"de contenu, il faut respecter certaines règles."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:75
msgid ""
"**Exact Text Match**: When searching for phrases, each word within the "
"phrase must be an exact match. No spelling variants are allowed. For "
"instance, a search for \"apple\" will not match with \"apples\"."
msgstr ""
"**Correspondance exacte** : Pour les phrases, chaque mot doit "
"correspondre exactement. Aucune variante orthographique n’est admise. Par"
" exemple, une recherche \"apple\" ne correspondra pas à \"apples\"."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:77
msgid ""
"**Case Sensitivity**: Searches are not case-sensitive. \"Cat\", \"cat\", "
"and \"CAT\" are all treated as the same."
msgstr ""
"**Sensibilité à la casse** : Les recherches ne sont pas sensibles à la "
"casse. \"Cat\", \"cat\" et \"CAT\" sont équivalents."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:79
msgid ""
"**Special Characters**: Certain special characters cannot be used in "
"search text."
msgstr ""
"**Caractères spéciaux** : Certains caractères spéciaux ne peuvent pas "
"être utilisés dans le texte de recherche."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:81
msgid ""
"**Wildcards**: The asterisk (*) can be used as a wildcard after a prefix "
"to broaden search results. For example, searching for \"choc\" retrieves "
"items with words like \"chocolate\", \"chocoholic\", etc."
msgstr ""
"**Jokers** : L’astérisque (*) peut être utilisé comme joker après un "
"préfixe pour élargir les résultats. Par exemple, rechercher \"choc\" "
"renvoie des éléments contenant \"chocolate\", \"chocoholic\", etc."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:83
msgid ""
"**Attachments**: System-readable file attachments are also included in "
"searches. These are files that can be converted to HTML, such as PDF "
"documents and text files."
msgstr ""
"**Pièces jointes** : Les pièces jointes lisibles par le système sont "
"également prises en compte. Il s’agit de fichiers pouvant être convertis "
"en HTML, comme les documents PDF ou les fichiers texte."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:85
msgid ""
"**Contacts in Address Books**: When searching for contacts, the entire "
"word or number string must be entered. For instance, to search contacts "
"by email address, the full address as it appears in the contact entry "
"must be used. It is not possible to search solely by domain."
msgstr ""
"**Contacts dans les carnets d’adresses** : La recherche de contacts "
"nécessite la saisie du mot ou de la chaîne numérique complète. Par "
"exemple, pour rechercher un contact par adresse e‑mail, il faut entrer "
"l’adresse exacte telle qu’elle apparaît dans le contact. La recherche par"
" domaine uniquement n’est pas possible."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:87
msgid ""
"**Search Language Structure**: Conducting content searches slightly "
"differs from text-match searches or typical word-processing features such"
" as Find."
msgstr ""
"**Structure du langage de recherche** : Les recherches de contenu "
"diffèrent légèrement des recherches par correspondance de texte ou des "
"fonctions classiques de traitement de texte comme Rechercher."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:89
msgid ""
"**Keywords**: If you know where to search for your item, you can enter "
"keywords followed by a colon and the search item in the search text box. "
"For example, \"in:inbox\"."
msgstr ""
"**Mots‑clés** : Si vous connaissez l’emplacement de l’élément, saisissez "
"un mot‑clé suivi de deux‑points et de l’élément recherché dans la zone de"
" texte. Par exemple, \"in:inbox\"."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:91
msgid "**Options:**"
msgstr "**Options :**"

#: ../../search/toc.rst:93
msgid ""
"**Content**: Specifies text that must be present in the message. Example:"
" content:important."
msgstr ""
"**Content** : Texte devant être présent dans le message. Exemple : "
"content:important."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:94
msgid ""
"**From**: Specifies a sender's name or email address. Example: "
"from:\"john.doe\"."
msgstr ""
"**From** : Nom ou adresse e‑mail de l’expéditeur. Exemple : "
"from:\"john.doe\"."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:95
msgid ""
"**To**: Similar to \"From:\", but for recipients in the To: header. "
"Example: to:\"jane.smith\"."
msgstr ""
"**To** : Identique à \"From\", mais pour les destinataires du champ To. "
"Exemple : to:\"jane.smith\"."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:96
msgid ""
"**CC**: Similar to \"From:\", but for recipients in the Cc: header. "
"Example: cc:\"Manager\"."
msgstr ""
"**CC** : Identique à \"From\", mais pour les destinataires du champ Cc. "
"Exemple : cc:\"Manager\"."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:97
msgid ""
"**Subject**: Specifies text that must appear in the subject header. "
"Example: subject:meeting."
msgstr ""
"**Subject** : Texte devant apparaître dans l’objet. Exemple : "
"subject:meeting."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:98
msgid "**In**: Specifies a folder. Example: in:sent."
msgstr "**In** : Dossier ciblé. Exemple : in:sent."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:99
msgid ""
"**Has**: Specifies an attribute that the message must have. Example: "
"has:attachment."
msgstr "**Has** : Attribut requis du message. Exemple : has:attachment."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:100
msgid ""
"**Filename**: Specifies an attachment file name. Example: "
"filename:report.pdf."
msgstr "**Filename** : Nom du fichier joint. Exemple : filename:report.pdf."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:101
msgid ""
"**Type**: Specifies a search within attachments of a specified type. "
"Example: type:excel."
msgstr ""
"**Type** : Recherche dans les pièces jointes d’un type donné. Exemple : "
"type:excel."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:102
msgid ""
"**Attachment**: Specifies any item with a certain type of attachment. "
"Example: attachment:word."
msgstr ""
"**Attachment** : Tout élément contenant un type de pièce jointe spécifié."
" Exemple : attachment:word."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:103
msgid "**Is**: Searches for messages with a specific status. Example: is:unread."
msgstr "**Is** : Recherche de messages avec un statut précis. Exemple : is:unread."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:104
msgid "**Date**: Specifies a date. Example: date:02/20/2024."
msgstr "**Date** : Date spécifiée. Exemple : date:02/20/2024."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:105
msgid ""
"**After**: Specifies mail sent after a certain date. Example: "
"after:01/01/2024."
msgstr ""
"**After** : Courriels envoyés après une date donnée. Exemple : "
"after:01/01/2024."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:106
msgid ""
"**Before**: Specifies mail sent before a certain date. Example: "
"before:03/01/2024."
msgstr ""
"**Before** : Courriels envoyés avant une date donnée. Exemple : "
"before:03/01/2024."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:107
msgid ""
"**Size**: Specifies emails based on their total size, including "
"attachments. Example: size: 1MB."
msgstr ""
"**Size** : Courriels selon leur taille totale, pièces jointes incluses. "
"Exemple : size: 1MB."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:108
msgid ""
"**Smaller**: Specifies emails based on their total size, including "
"attachments. Example: smaller:1MB."
msgstr ""
"**Smaller** : Courriels dont la taille totale, pièces jointes incluses, "
"est inférieure. Exemple : smaller:1MB."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:109
msgid ""
"**Larger**: Specifies emails based on their total size, including "
"attachments. Example: smaller:1MB."
msgstr ""
"**Larger** : Courriels dont la taille totale, pièces jointes incluses, "
"est supérieure. Exemple : smaller:1MB."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:110
msgid ""
"**Tag**: Finds messages tagged with a specified tag. Example: "
"tag:important."
msgstr ""
"**Tag** : Recherche de messages étiquetés avec le tag indiqué. Exemple : "
"tag:important."

#: ../../search/toc.rst:112
msgid ""
"**Wildcards**: The asterisk (*) after a prefix serves as a wildcard to "
"find content with words having similar spellings. For instance, \"dog\" "
"retrieves items with words like \"doggy\", \"doghouse\", etc. Note: "
"Double-byte asterisk signs in search queries are ignored during the "
"search."
msgstr ""
"**Wildcards** : L’astérisque (*) après un préfixe agit comme joker pour "
"retrouver du contenu contenant des mots aux orthographes similaires. Par "
"ex., \"dog\" renvoie les éléments contenant \"doggy\", \"doghouse\", etc."
" Remarque : les astérisques double octet sont ignorés dans les requêtes."

